\mid \left(\frac{-2}{3^2}\right)\mid<1
\lim_{n \to \infty} \frac{(-2)^n}{3^{2n}} = \lim_{n \to \infty} \frac{(-2)^n}{(3^2)^n} = \lim_{n \to \infty} \left(\frac{-2}{3^2}\right)^n
\Big|\dfrac{-2}{3^2}\Big| = \dfrac{2}{9}< 1
\lim_{n \to \infty} \left(\frac{-2}{3^2}\right)^n = 0.
